Texas Flip and Move - Season 1, Episode 6




Hardwood House vs. Stinky Disaster House

Cody Slay wins a house in White Settlement for $500, which he believes has mostly cosmetic problems. When he and Suzi tour the interior, their hearts sink: it is a disaster. Meanwhile, Randy wins a sweet little house in excellent condition on the exterior but with a big surprise inside.




Original Air Date: 13-Feb-2015
